'''沙龙·莫勒姆'''（{{lang-en|Sharon Moalem}}，{{bd||}}）是一位[[加拿大|加拿大]][[医生|医生]]、[[科学家|科学家]]和作家，出生于[[蒙特利尔|蒙特利尔]]，主要科普作品有《[[病者生存|病者生存：疾病如何延续人类寿命]]》（''Survival of the Sickest: The Surprising Connections Between Disease and Longevity''，与乔纳森·普林斯合著）、《基因革命：跑步、牛奶、童年经历如何改变我们的基因》（''Inheritance: How Our Genes Change Our Lives—And Our Lives Change Our Genes''）等<ref name=nyt>{{cite web|last=Blakeslee|first=Sandra|title=New Theory Places Origin of Diabetes in an Age of Icy Hardships|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/17/health/17diab.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|work=New York Times}}</ref><ref name=dailyshow>{{cite web|last=Stewart|first=Jon|title=Dr. Sharon Moalem|url=http://www.thedailyshow.com/watch/thu-march-8-2007/dr--sharon-moalem|publisher=The Daily Show|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2014-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226202642/http://www.thedailyshow.com/watch/thu-march-8-2007/dr--sharon-moalem|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=sundaytimes>{{cite news |last1=Appleyard |first1=Bryan |title=Dr Sharon Moalem: why women are the genetically stronger sex |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/dr-sharon-moalem-why-women-are-the-genetically-stronger-sex-zh2xlbvt8 |publisher=The Sunday Times |accessdate=2021-02-17 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123202529/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/dr-sharon-moalem-why-women-are-the-genetically-stronger-sex-zh2xlbvt8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

